item.title: Nephack 3.0
item.author: Author
item.description: Introduction Actually NepHack is one of the Biggest Hacking Competition of Nepal after threatcon which is especially CTF (Jeopardy type) competition which is held annually every year in K.U.( Kathmandu University), Dhulikhel, Nepal. But unfortunately this year due to some internal problem of K.U NepHack 3.0 was held in premises of Cynical Technology . Event happened at Jan 25–26,2020 but unfortunately I wasn’t able to attend due to my work .
